  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}Hey, what's wrong?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}So, you heard about Takaya and Jin, huh?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}I was planning on telling you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}I get that they were your friends, but we had to fight them.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 10 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
