  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_014_5_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 2 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}Don't touch me![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}Wha— Oh, I-I'm sorry. I didn't mean to...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="17" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 25 0 0}This is... too painful.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 26 0 0}It used to be fun when you came to visit.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 27 0 0}But now... it's different.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="18" name="MSG_017_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 28 0 0}Huh!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="19" name="MSG_018_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 29 0 0}It hurts inside. I can't breathe.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 201 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 30 0 0}I can't take this anymore![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="20" name="MSG_019_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 31 0 0}Wh-What do you mean!? I don't understand![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 32 0 0}Did I do something wrong? Tell me what it is![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
